a nice cookie,

00:33.182 --> 00:35.683
and the biggest
Mylar balloon they sold
at the grocery store.

00:35.751 --> 00:37.636
Wake up, man!
You're losing her!

00:37.703 --> 00:39.020
When did you talk
to Gloria?

00:39.087 --> 00:40.488
This afternoon.

00:40.556 --> 00:42.524
I'm just taking Claire up
to the overlook on Mulholland

00:42.592 --> 00:44.642
for a little old-school
make-out sesh.

00:44.710 --> 00:46.260
Oh, Phil.

00:46.328 --> 00:48.296
You're so good
at Valentine things...

00:48.364 --> 00:51.766
