like weirdos?

01:00.125 --> 01:01.943
It's not weird, Dad.
It's fun.

01:02.011 --> 01:03.828
Yeah. Tonight,
we get to be 17 again,

01:03.896 --> 01:05.312
when we were just
a couple of innocent,

01:05.379 --> 01:07.799
wide-eyed virgins.

01:07.866 --> 01:09.301
Shut up.

01:09.368 --> 01:10.735
I'm not doing it.

01:10.802 --> 01:11.986
